# üö´ Forbidden Practices

## ‚ùå Unscoped Data Access

Never read or write data without a `project_id` scope.

---

## ‚ùå Vendor Lock-in

Never call vendor SDKs directly from services.

---

## ‚ùå SDK Leakage

Never expose vendor models outside providers.

---

## ‚ùå Blocking AI Calls

Never execute OCR or embedding generation inside HTTP requests.

---

## ‚ùå Prompt Spaghetti

Never embed prompts directly inside business logic.

---

## ‚ùå Vector-only Retrieval

Always use Hybrid Retrieval.

---

## ‚ùå No Retry Policies

Every provider should support retries and graceful fallback.

---

## ‚ùå Silent Exceptions

Never swallow exceptions.

Always:

* Log Traceback
* Attach Trace ID
* Return Meaningful Errors
